cars.description: This is an immaculate 2006 Nissan Rogue with only 25000 miles on it. Leather seats, power everything. You truly will be a loan ranger when you cruise the open road in this sleek unique suv.

This is old classic is a beast in the streets. With one working window, no AC, and steering as loose as a swinging gate on a windy day you are sure to cook and fear for your life yet love every minute!
This is an immaculate 2006 Honda Pilot pronounced 'P Low'. Leather seats, power everything and AC that works great, you are sure to feel the upgrade from your previous 'classic'.
